                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-6">
                                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm" t-on-click="_onClickDriverAbsent">
                                    <div class="card-body text-center">
                                        <h5 class="card-title">Absent</h5>
